[b][color=mediumaquamarine][size=20]General Info[/size][/color][/b][/center][list][item]Store wine ((wine)) here to increase value.[/item][item]Wine value increases daily at [[Daily Reset]]. [s] You do not need to pet your wine.  Unless you want too, we won't judge you. There's just not a button. [/s][/item][item]Wine is sold directly from the cellar. Click the green button and you will receive the amount of silver shown.[/item][item]Negotiator perks do not apply. The sell price displayed is what you will receive when sold.[/item][item]Wine can be removed once it has been stored. However it will cost you the price it would sell for. For example, if a bottle is worth 6,345,721 silver, it would cost 6,345,721 to remove and put back in your inventory.[/item][item]Every 10 [[Tower]] levels increases the max value of a bottle of wine by 1 million. This happens at T11, T21, T31, etc. [/item][item]Once removed, the wine goes back to being just standard wine and will start back at zero if put back in the cellar[/item][item]See [[%Perks]]: Fancy Bottle, Cellar Insulation, Cellar Expansion I-IV and Wine-o-Matic for information on these upgrades[/item][item]Wine value formula:[/item][s]silver value = 1000 + (days in cellar^3 * farming level * cellar insulation bonus)
Cellar Insulation bonus is 1 without any Cellar Insulation perks, 3 with Cellar Insulation I, 6 with I and II, and 9 with I, II, and III.[/s][/list]
